<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>بَابُ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>مَرْفُوعَاتِ الأَسْمَاءِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>المَرْفُوعَاتُ سَبْعَةٌ؛<span style="color:#006d98"> وَهِيَ:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>الفَاعِلُ، وَالمَفْعُولُ الَّذِي لَمْ يُسَمَّ فَاعِلُهُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَالمُبْتَدَأُ، وَخَبَرُهُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَاسْمُ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«كَانَ»</span> وَأَخَوَاتِهَا، وَخَبَرُ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«إِنَّ»</span> وَأَخَوَاتِهَا.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَالتَّابِعُ لِلْمَرْفُوعِ -<span style="color:#006d98"> وَهُوَ أَرْبَعَةُ أَشْيَاءَ:</span> النَّعْتُ، وَالعَطْفُ، وَالتَّوْكِيدُ، وَالبَدَلُ ـ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>* * *<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>